<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-36-0706 </DOCNO><TEXT>Experimental results are presented on active-medium formation mechanismsin a laser with a sectioned plasma source of metal vapor (a SPER laser).The following processes were observed in the laser active medium: buffer-gaspreionization; mixing of metal vapor and buffer gas during plasma expansion;plasma-chemical reactions in the expanding plasma; and a collisionalmechanism of plasma cooling.</TEXT></DOC>